itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇怪唔明玄幻劇大陸興得起 係因為主力睇電視既係班侯生仔？</blockquote><br />\n你睇堆主角唔係鮮肉就小花<br />\n就知邊D人係睇劇主力啦"},{"pid":"021060459b741dda14e5bbeebf739b8790972413","tid":480484,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時都唔明點解佢同BABY兩個都算同期質素又唔係話好大差距<br />\n依家際遇可以咁唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個係小三上位記, 一個係搞自己一步一步捱出黎<br />\n點同呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算唔算係黃曉明捧人同黎明捧人既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBaby醒目識靠明哥<br />\n但jm就蠢啦 跟黎明"},{"pid":"92aa1cf15696bdee3facd4fcd6bc63381b0d2d13","tid":480484,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"jm完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da22b7c84642d36fbf1aab9989c467e618ab226b","tid":480484,"uid":42095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"Well~~ 真係嘥晒，明明jm最為人津津樂道嘅係佢一口港式港女單詞英文，如果可以運用埋應該會吸到仲多粉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0127430e788b06056c8b5d33a6129837bbf8482","tid":480484,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"呢套劇個trailer睇落好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e61b58d70643137b20928461ca541d3ed5c196c","tid":480484,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"好撚靚"}]}